title: Igor Ledochowski - How To Practice Hypnosis Without Fear
description:
Igor relied on these PROVEN strategies to change himself from a shy "wall flower" to a FEARLESS hypnotist working with hundreds of clients in his private practice...

And teaching thousands of people hypnosis from the podium during intense "can't-screw-up-or-they'll-know" live seminar events around the world.
! You can use these simple shortcuts to overcome ALL your fears, concerns and insecurities about becoming the best hypnotist you can be... in 21 days or less!
